  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The incidence of leucotrichia has been reported to range from 9 to 48.4% of all vitiligo
      patients.Leucotrichia is more often observed in segmental vitiligo with a very high
      percentage. However, further studies considering the prevalence of leucotrichia in different
      types of vitiligo need to be conducted.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
